{"tid":1291293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人該如何應對被引入社會信用系統？！","createTime":"2019-07-06T20:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T20:55:34.000Z","uid":72125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc3ed734c778b0a19cf0c2b180ac130434e1994","tid":1291293,"uid":72125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T20:21:36.000Z","msg":"粵推大灣區3年計劃 聚焦創科吸港青 加強粵港澳警務合作 加快建社會信用系統<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】中央2月發布《粵港澳大灣區發展規劃綱要》（下稱綱要）後，廣東近日推出具體措施，昨日公布《貫徹落實綱要的實施意見》（下稱意見），以及《廣東省推進粵港澳大灣區建設3年行動計劃（2018-2020年）》（下稱計劃），被視為粵方對於大灣區建設的「施工圖」和「任務書」。除建設國際科技創新中心外，還提出加強粵港澳警務合作交流，建立粵港澳突發事件應急處置聯動機制和應急協調平台，並加快建立社會信用體系。<br />\n//計劃又提到，要加快建立社會信用體系和市場監管體系建設；研究制定廣東省社會信用條例；探索依法對大灣區內企業聯動實施信用激勵和失信懲戒；建成全省統一的市場監管信息平台。//<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/article/20190706/s00013/1562350534968/%e7%b2%b5%e6%8e%a8%e5%a4%a7%e7%81%a3%e5%8d%803%e5%b9%b4%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83-%e8%81%9a%e7%84%a6%e5%89%b5%e7%a7%91%e5%90%b8%e6%b8%af%e9%9d%92-%e5%8a%a0%e5%bc%b7%e7%b2%b5%e6%b8%af%e6%be%b3%e8%ad%a6%e5%8b%99%e5%90%88%e4%bd%9c-%e5%8a%a0%e5%bf%ab%e5%bb%ba%e7%a4%be%e6%9c%83%e4%bf%a1%e7%94%a8%e7%b3%bb%e7%b5%b1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%2Farticle%2F20190706%2Fs00013%2F1562350534968%2F%25e7%25b2%25b5%25e6%258e%25a8%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e7%2581%25a3%25e5%258d%25803%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e8%25a8%2588%25e5%258a%2583-%25e8%2581%259a%25e7%2584%25a6%25e5%2589%25b5%25e7%25a7%2591%25e5%2590%25b8%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%259d%2592-%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e7%25b2%25b5%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%25be%25b3%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%2590%2588%25e4%25bd%259c-%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%25bf%25ab%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e7%25a4%25be%25e6%259c%2583%25e4%25bf%25a1%25e7%2594%25a8%25e7%25b3%25bb%25e7%25b5%25b1&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=1a204ef1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%2Farticle%2F20190706%2Fs00013%2F1562350534968%2F%25e7%25b2%25b5%25e6%258e%25a8%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e7%2581%25a3%25e5%258d%25803%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e8%25a8%2588%25e5%258a%2583-%25e8%2581%259a%25e7%2584%25a6%25e5%2589%25b5%25e7%25a7%2591%25e5%2590%25b8%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%259d%2592-%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e7%25b2%25b5%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%25be%25b3%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%2590%2588%25e4%25bd%259c-%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%25bf%25ab%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e7%25a4%25be%25e6%259c%2583%25e4%25bf%25a1%25e7%2594%25a8%25e7%25b3%25bb%25e7%25b5%25b1&h=3d03e1a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/article/20190706/s00013/1562350534968/%e7%b2%b5%e6%8e%a8%e5%a4%a7%e7%81%a3%e5%8d%803%e5%b9%b4%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83-%e8%81%9a%e7%84%a6%e5%89%b5%e7%a7%91%e5%90%b8%e6%b8%af%e9%9d%92-%e5%8a%a0%e5%bc%b7%e7%b2%b5%e6%b8%af%e6%be%b3%e8%ad%a6%e5%8b%99%e5%90%88%e4%bd%9c-%e5%8a%a0%e5%bf%ab%e5%bb%ba%e7%a4%be%e6%9c%83%e4%bf%a1%e7%94%a8%e7%b3%bb%e7%b5%b1</a>"},{"pid":"6c72453c632d23e806ce9a5225bb7f242590e86c","tid":1291293,"uid":72125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T20:25:14.000Z","msg":"原來鬼國2014年已經開始行緊，將所有人分等級A-D，排名低就無得出國，無得升職，無得置業，子女讀書不能入高排名學校"},{"pid":"50701e386fc96cde66acd49a8a840912c9c47a38","tid":1291293,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T20:47:18.000Z","msg":"共產黨打到黎 全港18區無得走<br />\n玉皇大帝都救唔到"},{"pid":"fb17bd425f4d1c5f61f478e82f50600f71aae4a1","tid":1291293,"uid":89834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T20:55:34.000Z","msg":"遲下有連登AC已經要扣一級先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}